definitions.definition: ( historical , measure ) A traditional Portuguese unit of liquid volume equal to 1.7–2.1 liters depending on the area of Portugal , used particularly for wine .

main_definition: ( historical , measure ) A traditional Portuguese unit of liquid volume equal to 1.7–2.1 liters depending on the area of Portugal , used particularly for wine .
